/* ŌöĆŌöĆ Editor Column ŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆ */
.editor-column {
  flex: 1;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  overflow: hidden;
}

/* ŌöĆŌöĆ Properties Panel ŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆ */
.properties-panel {
  position: relative;
  background: var(--color-bg-sidebar);
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  flex-shrink: 0;
  overflow: hidden;
  max-height: 56px;
  transition: max-height 0.2s ease, border-bottom-color 0.2s ease;
}

.properties-panel.closed {
  max-height: 0;
  border-bottom-color: transparent;
}

.properties-inner {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 12px;
  padding: 0 56px 0 24px;
  height: 56px;
  overflow: hidden;
}

.prop-field {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 5px;
  flex-shrink: 0;
}

.prop-label {
  font-size: 11px;
  color: var(--color-text-faint);
  text-transform: uppercase;
  letter-spacing: 0.04em;
}

